{
  "stem": "6845.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And if I liked it very much, or whoever admired it very much, really insisted for a little more finish, she would let me go to my room, and I could even paint it.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I grew up with this, and it was always a very, very important thing for me, that what it did to me-- to my ego-- that I could create these things.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was admired from early age.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So when people ask me, do you have any background with your s-- sculpting?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I say, well, bread.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I worked with br-- soft bread, and-- and that's the honest truth, that that's the way it started.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But eventually, I realized that I was-- like the embroidery, and crocheting, and just lots of, lots of things-- whatever could be done by hand, I-- I just wanted to do it.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was good at it and did it all my life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, not in Sobrance-- not there, no, because that was-- um, how-- if I was 11 in [LAUGHS] 1922-- no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That came much, much later.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went into the city because, already, my two brothers were living there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we paid-- so we found some nice family, and they accepted kids.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Sometimes they were together, sometimes separately.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so they can go to-- for higher education, gymnasium, or high school, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I was 11, I too was sent to Uzhorod.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The funny thing happened that, just before these times arrived, I met this couple from the city in our spa.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And a girl-- their daughter, Martha-- and I kind of fell for each other, and we-- oh!",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Such a love affair.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We shall never part.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we both made a resolution.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
